{"tid":2508595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯：認定中國官媒做「外國使團」　為揭資金來源","createTime":"2021-04-29T01:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T03:45:56.000Z","uid":227801,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"18b4f350a61fbd279108c2d19c5940d0cd5ad42c","tid":2508595,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:17:06.000Z","msg":"[url]https://www.881<del><a href=\"http://903.com/news/china/238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F238&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzRq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=4aa036d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">903.com/news/china/238</a></del>9342[/url]<br />\n中美角力｜布林肯：認定中國官媒做「外國使團」　為揭資金來源<br />\n<br />\n發佈時間 2021-04-29 08:20&nbsp;最後更新時間 2021-04-29 08:19<br />\n<br />\n美國去年加強審查中國官媒，中國環球電視網（CGTN）和中新社等多間中國傳媒遭列為「外國使團」，美國國務卿布林肯表示，美國並非要禁止中國官媒運作，將它們列為「外國使團」是想公眾了解這些傳媒的資金來源，又指控這些傳媒遭中國政府控制，專注於為北京作全球宣傳，傳達中共的意見，甚至造謠。<br />\n布林肯在世界新聞自由日前與外國傳媒交流，對於中國要求多間美國傳媒匯報在中國境內的運作，布林肯批評，在新聞自由問題上，中國同其他國家並非「互惠」，中國受惠於外界的開放傳媒環境，卻不讓他人受益，形容這種做法難以持續。"},{"pid":"e216186eb888991d059da3473e3e6b5b00d63555","tid":2508595,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c355c50c765ea75e9cdf4708767199593d8e561a","tid":2508595,"uid":298523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"一早就要做"},{"pid":"679fc26d9c8c8a19bea4eed4235a4670bcfec7de","tid":2508595,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"乙己學院<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55a28a26c14437f3fc72f306e8a3620da309b06","tid":2508595,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c799fdfeea8ef4600fc64604a0dcc6ea61a5333c","tid":2508595,"uid":227801,"l